In fact, was getting severely bullied ouliec from 7th grade up until finishing high school. A few times it got to the point where we had to get the police involved.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax Although school wasn't really an easy time for me, looking back, those times made me more independent and sparked my interest in business and personal development.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In high school, came across a social media marketing agency course. I realized could start that business because it didn't require a huge starting capital and could do it while was still at school. So I started my own agency.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 12, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In my last year of high school, started making $1-3K per month with my agency. It was nothing special but it was decent money at the time and it solidified that could eventually pursue my business full time.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on September 12, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax So in the final year of high school, had two options, either go to university or learn a trade.
